message: I'm excited to offer you this great product, and I think you'll really love it. I'm willing to let it go for $120.
That's a bit higher than I was hoping for. I'm interested, but I can only go up to $85.
I understand you're looking for a better deal, but I've got to make a profit. I'm willing to meet you in the middle at $110.
I appreciate you coming down a bit, but $110 is still a little too high for me.  I'm sticking with my offer of $85.
